{"tid":922967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200員工要求停研審查搜尋器　斥Google見錢開眼","createTime":"2018-11-30T21:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T02:35:29.000Z","uid":53524,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12401562f54eb9f8dde5eea3bf4e698046e74545","tid":922967,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T21:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20181128/photo/bkn-20181128090513389-1128_00972_001_02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20181128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181128090513389-1128_00972_001_02p.jpg&h=7631f9ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國互聯網企業Google早前被揭發為中國市場，開發具有審查功能的搜尋器「蜻蜓」（Dragonfly），不但引起人權組織關注，內部的反對聲音亦不絕。超過200名員工於周二（27日）發公開信，要求Google停止研發「蜻蜓」，指公司已變得「見錢開眼」。<br />\n<br />\n早於今年8月，1400名Google員工已聯署要求公司，改善監管包括「蜻蜓」在內等有道德問題或爭議的研發項目。在今次的公開信中，聯署者包括工程師、設計師及管理層人員，部分人認為該情況只有輕微進展，又關注中國政府以搜尋數據追蹤異見分子，以及透過控制網上內容打壓真相。<br />\n<br />\n公開信寫道：「我們反對科技用來協助強權打壓弱勢。」聯署者表示，他們不再相信公司願意把價值觀放在首位，現時變得只重視利潤。他們又列出今年多宗令人失望的事件，包括Google承認向涉及性騷擾的高層，支付一筆龐大的離職費。Google拒絕回應公開信。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，國際特赦組織於同日發起公眾聯署，呼籲Google取消「蜻蜓」，而該組織成員亦在全球多地的Google辦公室及總部外示威。中國工業和信息化部一名官員向英國傳媒表示，暫未有迹象顯示Google調整推出「蜻蜓」的計劃，但形容它於明年發布是不切實際。"},{"pid":"be8b16e27ef3de36fc4993cc964f6cebe805bc38","tid":922967,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"Do no evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b7ea12b25de9ff5d8c7c02c9081e2befa29200","tid":922967,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:28:12.000Z","msg":"好彩你請得多左膠咋，自己奶返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247ce8cdf9c98e4459b68227e28e3a1c6a1f7e95","tid":922967,"uid":156771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8b16e27ef3de36fc4993cc964f6cebe805bc38","tid":922967,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"Do no evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil<br />\n過去為Google的企業座右銘及口號，已不在經營準則中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f96930de93b8b308ecd6b530eabdacb54207c9f","tid":922967,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"247ce8cdf9c98e4459b68227e28e3a1c6a1f7e95","tid":922967,"uid":156771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8b16e27ef3de36fc4993cc964f6cebe805bc38","tid":922967,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"Do no evil<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:30:28.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil<br />\n過去為Google的企業座右銘及口號，已不在經營準則中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.dazeinfo.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Google-dont-be-evil1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.dazeinfo.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F04%2FGoogle-dont-be-evil1.jpg&h=ae32183f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}